<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= nama %> | Excellence in Education</title>
    
    <!-- CSS & Fonts Mewah -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net">

    <style>
        :root { --primary: #0f172a; --accent: #2563eb; --light: #f8fafc; }
        body { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; background-color: var(--light); color: var(--primary); }
        
        /* Hero Section ala Perusahaan Besar */
        .hero { 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, #1e293b 100%); 
            color: white; padding: 160px 0 120px 0; 
            border-radius: 0 0 60px 60px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .navbar-brand { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -1px; color: white !important; }
        
        .card-pro { 
            border: none; border-radius: 28px; transition: 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275); 
            background: white; padding: 45px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.03); height: 100%;
        }
        .card-pro:hover { transform: translateY(-12px); box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
        
        .icon-box { 
            width: 70px; height: 70px; background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1); 
            color: var(--accent); border-radius: 20px; display: flex; 
            align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .btn-cta { 
            background-color: var(--accent); border: none; padding: 16px 40px; 
            border-radius: 16px; font-weight: 700; transition: 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2);
        }
        .btn-cta:hover { transform: scale(1.05); background-color: #1d4ed8; color: white; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-dark bg-transparent position-absolute w-100 pt-4">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#"><i class="bi bi-shield-check me-2"></i>NURUL HIDAYAH</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="hero text-center">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-lg-10">
                    <span class="badge rounded-pill bg-primary bg-opacity-25 text-primary px-3 py-2 mb-4">Penerimaan Siswa Baru 2026</span>
                    <h1 class="display-2 fw-bold mb-4">Mendidik Generasi,<br><span class="text-info">Membangun Peradaban.</span></h1>
                    <p class="lead mb-5 opacity-75 px-lg-5">Portal resmi pendidikan modern berbasis nilai-nilai luhur dan inovasi teknologi.</p>
                    <a href="mailto:<%= email %>" class="btn btn-cta text-white">Konsultasi Pendidikan <i class="bi bi-arrow-right ms-2"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="container my-5 py-5">
        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card-pro">
                    <div class="icon-box"><i class="bi bi-lightning-charge"></i></div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold">Kurikulum Unggul</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Integrasi kurikulum nasional dengan standar internasional yang adaptif terhadap masa depan.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card-pro">
                    <div class="icon-box"><i class="bi bi-star"></i></div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold">Fasilitas Modern</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Laboratorium IT canggih, perpustakaan digital, dan lingkungan belajar yang inspiratif.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card-pro">
                    <div class="icon-box"><i class="bi bi-heart"></i></div>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold">Pembinaan Karakter</h4>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Fokus pada pembentukan akhlakul karimah dan kemandirian setiap peserta didik.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-5 text-center bg-white border-top">
        <div class="container">
            <p class="text-muted small mb-0 fw-bold">&copy; 2026 <%= nama %> Official Portal. Managed with Node.js v22.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
